{"tid":2499332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"張智霖已接種第一劑科興疫苗：我身體OK 感覺還好","createTime":"2021-04-21T22:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T23:18:19.000Z","uid":230530,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40199c115d651d75182a19af14430bbb96e80e13","tid":2499332,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:27:47.000Z","msg":"Chilam坦言接到無綫監製邀請「幫手」拍劇，他說：「呢位大監製，去年11月已邀請我2022年拍一部劇集續集，他那麼早邀請我，我都被打動到，很感興趣，會先睇監製作品。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChilam之前返內地拍梁家樹監製的劇集《家族榮耀》，稍後會再回內地工作，最近已打第一劑科興疫苗做準備：「我平時身體OK，感覺還好。」他自言有幽閉恐懼症，每次返內地要接受14日隔離，對他是好大難關，所以要考慮很久才接工作。"},{"pid":"473b2e9290cefc2b1cc3467b033067b2c22c0eec","tid":2499332,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:57:12.000Z","msg":"幾時打第二針？"},{"pid":"7df135469cf0f93b8fbd09a473a0437786bcaa16","tid":2499332,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"473b2e9290cefc2b1cc3467b033067b2c22c0eec","tid":2499332,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:57:12.000Z","msg":"幾時打第二針？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"最好聽日, 越早打越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669d5633442392107745f0fa13159143d554015e","tid":2499332,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"痴lam人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}